-----------------------------------------

Code for a Monte Carlo (MC) approach for calculating secondary
electron emission (SEE) from metal surfaces

Description of repository contents:
 mcsee.py: module containing MCsee methods and class definitions
 mcsee_driver.py: script used to perform MCsee calculations
 example/: directory containing example with necessary input files

Requirements:
 numpy
 methods & quantities from modules in pymods/
  - either ensure local versions are up to date or copy to source
    directory to use directly

